018-05-27T13:25:52.000Z","msg":"抑鬱對於某d人死左仲好<br />\n但無事既人就永遠迫佢繼續生存 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035cde53594fcb7f8230d8fb575b74012dcaaafe","tid":680413,"uid":82317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"唔通你想直接用落人身上試？<br />\n我就話動物試藥係必要<br />\n唔理佢有冇用都好，如果冇用咪冇用囉<br />\n如果有用咁人類咪受小啲苦"},{"pid":"c689ab93e6baf7944168953a9026b90bda18a07d","tid":680413,"uid":51297,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d165216dec295f6135c270f459112af37896a05f","tid":680413,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:00:31.000Z","msg":"巴打, 想問吓如果想讀心理學入門的書, 有冇邊本介紹?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為想讀心理學, 想睇自己啱唔啱<br />\n有LIKE樓主FB page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:57:21.000Z","msg":"多謝支持！巴打！<br />\n<br />\n我個人推介葉重新嘅&lt;心理學&gt; 大學入門程度教科書泥<br />\n<br />\n如果想易入口少少可以睇一冊通曉心理學<br />\n<br />\n學左d基本先，再跟興趣睇 有本叫 the rightous mind講道德心理學 超精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a187ae1c2d0eb6f29214e1a039a137ae0b006bd","tid":680413,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n食過一排SSRI 覺得個自信感好唔自在<br />\n靠行山開心咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n精神科其實點定義所謂微笑抑鬱症<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得我算係呢個狀態  抑鬱既意念已經係我既內在思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我好認同我一無是處但我又無乜自殺念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad5fb54a2bd451cabc4652327ddbcd56bb6eb6e","tid":680413,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b9ae9bab085d2f426cd4fcfb4130ac5b0f0d2cc","tid":680413,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:24:19.000Z","msg":"笑吓咪得，洗乜食藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\